^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|If you are deciding between a more conservative and less conservative bid. With a nine card fit, choose the less conservative bid (limit raise in this case). With an eight card fit, choose the more conservative bid. A nine card fit is worth at least half a trick compared to an eight card fit. So, here I would content myself with a 2S bid.|
