^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|First, as I mentioned the club stopper is iffy. Second, the hand is a bit strong for 1N but not quite good enough for 2N. Thus, in order to encourage partner to bid again, South  might choose 2D. Partner might pass and that might indeed be the best contract. But, if partner has hearts, or a good hand, partner will take another bid.|
