^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Because this was such a long auction, West has a lot of information about North's hand and South's hand as well based on the auction. It is clear North is short in clubs and that North has exactly 3 hearts and 4 spades. North's most likely distribution is 4-3-5-1, or possibly 4-3-6-0. Normally that might call for a trump lead, and, in fact, that might work out well. But, West is an expert defender.|
