NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|I would not expect you to work this out, but West is pretty sure that she can beat declarer. Remember, South raised North's diamonds, therefore, because North has long diamonds, and South  has at least three. Thus, North/south have an eight card diamond fit or perhaps even a 9 card fit. They probably have an eight card heart fit which means partner has three hearts. Further, because West has four diamonds, and North/south have at least eight, partner has at most a singleton diamond.|
