^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Remember, when leading something for partner to trump, the spot you lead is "suit preference." If West leads a high diamond back, that is telling East to lead the higher of the two non-trump suits back, in this case spades. If West leads a low diamond back, that asks for the lower of the non-trump suits back, a club in this case. Without the suit preference, East would have to guess which black suit to lead back. But, by following the suit preference, East knows to lead back a club for the second diamond ruff.|
